node.text:
Use this easy trick if you don’t fancy your home lighting. Off all light to get a pitch black (if you have natural lighting aka window in the room, do it in evening time, I did mine at 8pm). Be creative and create any shape for your lighting effect, circle, star, triangle, you name it! If you’re not feeling crafty, just use toilet paper roll for the circle effect, it will do the magic too 🤓 *I used circle for my profile pic and set it to B&W tone
.
